T1  - The Gendering of Job Postings in the Online Recruitment Process
AU  - Castilla, Emilio J.
AU  - Rho, Hye Jin
Y1  - 2023/02/27
PY  - 2023
DA  - 2023/11/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2023.4674
