T1  - The Longshot Bias Is a Context Effect
AU  - Meyer, Andrew
AU  - Hundtofte, Sean
Y1  - 2023/04/07
PY  - 2023
DA  - 2023/11/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2023.4684
